OL,3,CLush founder predicts The Body Shop
OL,4,Cwill close stores
OL,6,FThree months ago, the German private
OL,7,Fequity firm Aurelius was celebrating
OL,8,Fthe acquisition of and pledging to
OL,9,F"return it to its former glory".
OL,11,FSince then, the majority of The Body
OL,12,FShop's operations in mainland Europe
OL,13,Fand part of the business in Asia have
OL,14,Fbeen sold off for an undisclosed sum
OL,15,Fto an unnamed buyer.
OL,17,FToday, - no longer able to pay its
OL,18,Fbills as they fall due.
