OL,3,CLush founder predicts The Body Shop
OL,4,Cwill close stores
OL,6,FA source close to Aurelius explains
OL,7,Fthat The Body Shop has proved to be in
OL,8,Ffar worse financial shape than was
OL,9,Fclear last November when the takeover
OL,10,Fwas agreed and that trading over
OL,11,FChristmas was dismal.
OL,13,FBoth of these things are plausible -
OL,14,FThe Body Shop's troubles date back
OL,15,Fyears not months - although Aurelius
OL,16,Fhas not provided any details.
OL,18,FAurelius bought The Body Shop as part
OL,19,Fof an "accelerated sales process".
