OL,3,CLush founder predicts The Body Shop
OL,4,Cwill close stores
OL,6,FThe previous owner, Natura, a
OL,7,FBrazilian company which bought The
OL,8,FBody Shop from L'Oreal for #880
OL,9,Fmillion in 2017, was keen to sell.
OL,11,FWe don't know how the eventual deal
OL,12,Fbetween Aurelius and Natura was
OL,13,Fstructured.
OL,15,FThe agreement valued The Body Shop at
OL,16,F#207 million but this is not the cash
OL,17,Fsum that Aurelius paid and it included
OL,18,Fan earn out clause of #90 million
OL,19,Fwhich would only apply if the company
OL,20,Fwent on to hit certain performance
OL,21,Ftargets.
