OL,3,CLush founder predicts The Body Shop
OL,4,Cwill close stores
OL,6,FSuffice to say, it hasn't. A judge has
OL,7,Fnow appointed FRP Advisory to take
OL,8,Fcontrol of the business and decide on
OL,9,Fthe best way forward.
OL,11,FIn a statement, FRP says they "will
OL,12,Fcontinue to trade the business in
OL,13,Fadministration, ensuring customers
OL,14,Fwill be able to continue to shop in
OL,15,Fstore and online".
OL,17,FPlan A will be to find a buyer willing
OL,18,Fto take on all 199 UK shops and the
OL,19,F2000 staff. But such an outcome seems
OL,20,Fhighly unlikely.
