OL,3,CLush founder predicts The Body Shop
OL,4,Cwill close stores
OL,6,FThe most recent set of accounts show
OL,7,Fthat The Body Shop's sales in the UK
OL,8,Fdropped by 30% during 2022 to #197
OL,9,Fmillion. The Body Shop group made a
OL,10,Floss of #71 million.
OL,12,FBut we don't know how loss-making the
OL,13,FUK business is currently or how much
OL,14,Fdebt it has.
OL,16,FMark Constantine, who used to supply
OL,17,FThe Body Shop and went on to found its
OL,18,Frival Lush, thinks the business will
OL,19,Fsurvive administration but that just
OL,20,Fover half of the UK shops are likely
OL,21,Fto close.
