OL,3,CLush founder predicts The Body Shop
OL,4,Cwill close stores
OL,6,FHe points out that another business
OL,7,FAurelius owned, Lloyds Pharmacy, ended
OL,8,Fup being liquidated last month after
OL,9,FAurelius parcelled-up the pharmacies
OL,10,Fand sold them to other companies.
OL,12,F"So it's anyone's guess what will
OL,13,Fhappen with The Body Shop,"
OL,14,FConstantine told ITV News.
OL,16,F"I don't believe The Body Shop has a
OL,17,Ffuture as online only," he added.
