OL,3,CLush founder predicts The Body Shop
OL,4,Cwill close stores
OL,6,FA source close to Aurelius has
OL,7,Fconfirmed to me that the private
OL,8,Fequity firm has security over a
OL,9,F"small" part of The Body Shop's debt.
OL,11,FThis matters because it means that,
OL,12,Fduring the insolvency process,
OL,13,FAurelius will be classed as a creditor
OL,14,Fand will be able to influence what
OL,15,Fhappens next.
