OL,6,FOne possible outcome is that the
OL,7,Fadministrator restructures the
OL,8,Fbusiness by cutting costs
OL,9,F(renegotiating contracts with
OL,10,Flandlords, closing shops and making
OL,11,Fstaff redundant) and then hands it
OL,12,Fback to Aurelius.
